description "Ewok

Class: Hero
Brief Overview: 
A small bowman and spear wielder carrying powerful/magical stones that deal intense knockback. 

^2Weaponry:
- Melee 
- Spear 
-- Based on Lightsaber
-- Yellow/Red/Purple styles
-- 50% lower damage
-- 53% shorter length
-- 33% wider radius
- Stones
-- Based on Frag Grenades (2)
-- Alt. fire only
-- Detonate on contact with surfaces
- Bow 
-- Based on T-21 (1)
-- Low maximum ammo

^8Attributes:
- Heal (1)
- Reinforcements (2)
- Assemble

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dash (2) [Class Special 2]
- Quickthrow (2) [Class Special 3 outside grenades]

Ewoks were a diminutive species of furry bipeds native to the forest moon of Endor. A large community of Ewoks assisted the Rebel Alliance in defeating the Galactic Empire at the Battle of Endor."